caption.p:
BLI binding kinetics of select CC25 and CC84 mAbs to monomeric RBDs derived from sarbecovirus clades: clade 1b (SARS-CoV-2, RatG13, Pang17), clade 1a (SARS-CoV-2, WIV1, SHC014), clade 3 (BM-4831, BtKY72) and clade 2 ((RmYN02, Rf1, Rs4081, Yun11). Binding kinetics were obtained using the 1:1 binding kinetics fitting model on ForteBio Data Analysis software and maximum binding responses, dissociations constants (K
D) and on-rate (kon
) and off-rate constants (koff
) for each antibody protein interaction are shown. KD, kon and koff values were calculated only for antibody-antigen interactions where a maximum binding response of 0.05nm was obtained.
